..TEXT:
|piota~: "Sole of the foot," i.e., foundation.  (Cf.
^Inf.~ XIX, 120.)  Elsewhere the term |radice~ is applied to
Cacciaguida (^Par.~ XV, 89), and |ceppo~ is used in referring to
another family (^Par.~ XVI, 106).
