|ma pria che 'l Guasco l'alto Arrigo inganni~:
Before 1312, when the Gascon pope, Clement V, after promising to
support the emperor, Henry VII, in his expedition to Italy,
promoted opposition to it.  See ^Inf.~ XIX, 83; ^Par.~ XXX,
133-148.
