..TEXT:
|pur l'anime che son di fama note~: Cacciaguida's
assertion here cannot be taken as literally true, for every
reader will recall the many humble, unknown characters
encountered in Hell and elsewhere.  One has only to think of the
riff-raff, generally, of the eighth circle of Inferno.
